\u201d Ready4S \u201d) and the Client as named in the signature column below.Ready4S and Client are sometimes collectively referred to herein as the \u201d Parties \u201d and individually as a \u201d Party \u201d.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 0, "end_char_idx": 345, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "c6584b69-8ef0-4b90-bb86-324558689020": {"__data__": {"id_": "c6584b69-8ef0-4b90-bb86-324558689020", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "bb93a6f2-b371-4267-9370-3522ea6c950d", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "f23898c97540d82c48482bf979dcf2ca7d57706e0217b4fb5d89993f0ad7dbe9", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "0ac27552-182b-4850-bf25-8c642d970a1a", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "7d8ef612fce4642f7fa5a56e337a3e1d23cab649f2aa9a00597e674113cdf12e", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "38eaa2f9-b354-44ff-b100-1a5373074621", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "9ef0d2c93ca42eba4998765bf759d1b89983de0e2a700c899eeb18c29c9ca7c6", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "A Party includes the entity named herein, its successors and assigns, any of its present or future corporate parents, subsidiaries, and organizations controlled by, controlling or under common control with such Party.Each of the Parties may be the \u201d Disclosing Party \u201d and the other party will be deemed to be the \u201d Receiving Party \u201d.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 348, "end_char_idx": 682, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "38eaa2f9-b354-44ff-b100-1a5373074621": {"__data__": {"id_": "38eaa2f9-b354-44ff-b100-1a5373074621", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "bb93a6f2-b371-4267-9370-3522ea6c950d", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "f23898c97540d82c48482bf979dcf2ca7d57706e0217b4fb5d89993f0ad7dbe9", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "c6584b69-8ef0-4b90-bb86-324558689020", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "4d31e2fc337bb9603fc237da208d62a3f14a92b00e96a793b00958e0d8ace840", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "179790dc-b3fe-49aa-aff1-413f98abb36c", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "a02017cb6819da229e8e61abaae0c81c3475f04856ce0fe0fc46dc31c13cd397", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "RECITALS\n\nA. The Parties intend to enter into discussions regarding a potential future business relationship; and\n\nB.\n\n In order to facilitate those discussions the Parties may wish to disclose to each other certain Confidential Information (as herein defined).\n\nTHEREFORE, it is agreed as follows:\n\n1 De\ufb01nitions and Interpretation\n\n1.1 1.1 In this Agreement: Confidential Information means:-\n\n(a) information relating to the Disclosing Party regarding its business, partners,", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 684, "end_char_idx": 1160, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "179790dc-b3fe-49aa-aff1-413f98abb36c": {"__data__": {"id_": "179790dc-b3fe-49aa-aff1-413f98abb36c", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "bb93a6f2-b371-4267-9370-3522ea6c950d", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "f23898c97540d82c48482bf979dcf2ca7d57706e0217b4fb5d89993f0ad7dbe9", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "38eaa2f9-b354-44ff-b100-1a5373074621", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "9ef0d2c93ca42eba4998765bf759d1b89983de0e2a700c899eeb18c29c9ca7c6", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "8db7078d-dd2f-4f79-8d2d-64d788449672", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "5d1bb685ebcdda59a0c0ca5e515109dbb4ac3a94ec5b9d18524cef4abf8a4ef1", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "customers or financial affairs (including details relating to any software the copyright in respect of which is vested in the Disclosing Party) which is obtained by the Receiving Party, either before or after this undertaking is entered into and either in writing or orally from or pursuant to the discussions with the Personnel of the Disclosing Party;\n\n(b) those portions of analyses, compilations, studies,", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 1163, "end_char_idx": 1572, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "8db7078d-dd2f-4f79-8d2d-64d788449672": {"__data__": {"id_": "8db7078d-dd2f-4f79-8d2d-64d788449672", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "bb93a6f2-b371-4267-9370-3522ea6c950d", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "f23898c97540d82c48482bf979dcf2ca7d57706e0217b4fb5d89993f0ad7dbe9", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "179790dc-b3fe-49aa-aff1-413f98abb36c", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "a02017cb6819da229e8e61abaae0c81c3475f04856ce0fe0fc46dc31c13cd397", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "b3c5fe38-948a-41ee-bdd6-5036b0089f4c", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "ec8403b7e1438c46282a8c8804b236a600d661ca04f2444e80d2c9d0a4cb9c34", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "reports and other documents prepared by the Disclosing Party which contain or otherwise reflect or are generated from any such information as is specified in paragraph (a) above;\n\n(c) information of a commercially sensitive nature relating to the Disclosing Party obtained by observation during any visits to the Disclosing Party\u2019s premises but subject always to the proviso set out in clause.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 1575, "end_char_idx": 1968, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "b3c5fe38-948a-41ee-bdd6-5036b0089f4c": {"__data__": {"id_": "b3c5fe38-948a-41ee-bdd6-5036b0089f4c", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "bb93a6f2-b371-4267-9370-3522ea6c950d", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "f23898c97540d82c48482bf979dcf2ca7d57706e0217b4fb5d89993f0ad7dbe9", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "8db7078d-dd2f-4f79-8d2d-64d788449672", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "5d1bb685ebcdda59a0c0ca5e515109dbb4ac3a94ec5b9d18524cef4abf8a4ef1", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "02b0fc07-87aa-471c-abc8-0c4109e6b8b1", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "54e3ebe4e17200e001f9c0bd67a23bee4662ee1267e7e6e9e14c2e9e6b1a567f", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "Disclosing Party means the Party whose Confidential Information is disclosed to the Receiving Party\nPersonnel means any and all staff, employees, directors, officers and professional advisors of a Party\nPurpose means any and all discussions and negotiations relating to a potential agreement between the Parties hereto as more particularly set out in Recital (A)\nReceiving Party means the Party who is in receipt of Confidential Information\n\n2 The Commitment\n\n2.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 1970, "end_char_idx": 2432, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "02b0fc07-87aa-471c-abc8-0c4109e6b8b1": {"__data__": {"id_": "02b0fc07-87aa-471c-abc8-0c4109e6b8b1", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "bb93a6f2-b371-4267-9370-3522ea6c950d", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "f23898c97540d82c48482bf979dcf2ca7d57706e0217b4fb5d89993f0ad7dbe9", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "b3c5fe38-948a-41ee-bdd6-5036b0089f4c", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "ec8403b7e1438c46282a8c8804b236a600d661ca04f2444e80d2c9d0a4cb9c34", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "04dd76f6-9493-4600-9b93-a983642355f6", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "e885d9a25bd32828c2834a5e3b8a586afa1e880a78c8c58fa08a370262e2b526", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "1 In consideration of each Party agreeing to supply the other Party with Confidential Information for the Purpose, and in consideration of the mutual undertakings set out herein the Parties each hereby separately agree and irrevocably undertake to each other that they will only use Confidential Information for the Purpose and otherwise to act in accordance with the terms and conditions hereinafter contained.\n\n2.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 2434, "end_char_idx": 2849, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "04dd76f6-9493-4600-9b93-a983642355f6": {"__data__": {"id_": "04dd76f6-9493-4600-9b93-a983642355f6", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "bb93a6f2-b371-4267-9370-3522ea6c950d", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "f23898c97540d82c48482bf979dcf2ca7d57706e0217b4fb5d89993f0ad7dbe9", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "02b0fc07-87aa-471c-abc8-0c4109e6b8b1", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "54e3ebe4e17200e001f9c0bd67a23bee4662ee1267e7e6e9e14c2e9e6b1a567f", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "a65f957b-fad4-42aa-8afe-25aab1649ec3", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "83b94dca4f9b03b0e6d87d65256bbe3684c5ee4c3db8eb96ca3227761be90c2f", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "2 The disclosure of Confidential Information by the Disclosing Party to the Receiving Party shall in no way be construed to imply any transfer of rights connected with the Confidential Information including, without limitation, any trade marks or business secrets.\n\n2.\n\n3 A Receiving Party\u2019s obligations in respect of Confidential Information made available by the Disclosing Party pursuant to this Agreement shall continue notwithstanding the termination of the Purpose.\n\n3 Safekeeping\n\n3.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 2851, "end_char_idx": 3341, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "a65f957b-fad4-42aa-8afe-25aab1649ec3": {"__data__": {"id_": "a65f957b-fad4-42aa-8afe-25aab1649ec3", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "bb93a6f2-b371-4267-9370-3522ea6c950d", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "f23898c97540d82c48482bf979dcf2ca7d57706e0217b4fb5d89993f0ad7dbe9", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "04dd76f6-9493-4600-9b93-a983642355f6", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "e885d9a25bd32828c2834a5e3b8a586afa1e880a78c8c58fa08a370262e2b526", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "db003a0d-fd54-4126-9793-2452058cba22", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "b2846aff6b4af4c9395d120254e51a2dbd1baf05b8f5b5da372782818272d429", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "1 A Receiving Party shall treat and safeguard as private and confidential all of the Confidential Information and will take all reasonable precautions in dealing with any Confidential Information so as to prevent any third party from having access to the Confidential Information.2\n\n4 Limited internal dissemination\n\n4.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 3343, "end_char_idx": 3662, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "db003a0d-fd54-4126-9793-2452058cba22": {"__data__": {"id_": "db003a0d-fd54-4126-9793-2452058cba22", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "bb93a6f2-b371-4267-9370-3522ea6c950d", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "f23898c97540d82c48482bf979dcf2ca7d57706e0217b4fb5d89993f0ad7dbe9", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "a65f957b-fad4-42aa-8afe-25aab1649ec3", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "83b94dca4f9b03b0e6d87d65256bbe3684c5ee4c3db8eb96ca3227761be90c2f", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "1f7a3aa1-689a-4be8-b9dc-ec1bd8c9ad95", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "8641196014268ef1625ee7065a4dbc26dbff2b7a3c79de8ea05991ad9f3fce86", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "1 A Receiving Party shall only disclose or reveal any Confidential Information disclosed to it to those of its Personnel who are required in the course of their duties to receive and consider the same in so far as is necessary to fulfil the Purpose.\n\n4.2 Prior to the disclosure of any Confidential Information to any such Personnel,\n\n the Receiving Party shall inform them of the confidential nature of the material and of the provisions of this confidentiality undertaking and obtain written confirmation of their acceptance of these terms.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 3664, "end_char_idx": 4206, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "1f7a3aa1-689a-4be8-b9dc-ec1bd8c9ad95": {"__data__": {"id_": "1f7a3aa1-689a-4be8-b9dc-ec1bd8c9ad95", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "bb93a6f2-b371-4267-9370-3522ea6c950d", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "f23898c97540d82c48482bf979dcf2ca7d57706e0217b4fb5d89993f0ad7dbe9", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "db003a0d-fd54-4126-9793-2452058cba22", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "b2846aff6b4af4c9395d120254e51a2dbd1baf05b8f5b5da372782818272d429", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "a99dc4f9-4850-4161-96c3-412536d9da5d", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "e1050b9f5af0f1ff72c52d9e38b466e628e63d07e686e1ac285c796aceeda9d3", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "5 Non-disclosure to third parties\n\n5.1 Save as otherwise permitted herein, a Receiving Party shall not,\n\n and shall procure that its Personnel do not, at any time without the Disclosing Party\u2019s prior written consent:\n\n(a) disclose the Confidential Information to any third party, either directly or indirectly; or\n\n indirectly; or\n\n(b) disclose to any person: -\n\n(i) the fact that discussions or negotiations are taking place between the Parties;", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 4208, "end_char_idx": 4654, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "a99dc4f9-4850-4161-96c3-412536d9da5d": {"__data__": {"id_": "a99dc4f9-4850-4161-96c3-412536d9da5d", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationsh